      "content": "it's not that simple though. counselors, small steps... it's been years of that and the hole just gets deeper. every time I think I've made progress, another bill comes or the interest just eats everything up. it feels like a trap. i'm just tired of fighting a battle that's already lost. i feel like i'm just existing in this loop of misery and it's never gonna end.",
